---

<Layout title="Ultro Robotics" expandedNav="true">
	<div
		id="landing"
		class="h-screen flex justify-center items-center bg-gradient-to-b from-black from-30% to-ultro-red-950 to-90%"
	>
		<p class="text-white">insert landing graphic here</p>
	</div>
	<div class="bg-ultro-red-950 h-96 flex justify-center items-center">
		<section
			id="about"
			class="text-white text-2xl w-4/5 max-w-192 text-center space-y-8"
		>
			<p>
				Team Ultro is a <strong><i>FIRST </i>Tech Challenge</strong> (FTC)
				robotics team based in <a
					href="https://browning.edu"
					class="underline hover:text-gray-300">The Browning School</a
				>, a New York City all-boys school. Our team name means "of its
				own mind" in Latin and represents our focus on <strong
					>student-led</strong
				>, innovative designs, and high-performing autonomous projects.
			</p>
			<p>
				Guided by mentors, our ultimate goal is to use FIRST Tech
				Challenge-learned skills to <strong
					>engineer for humanity.</strong>
			</p>
		</section>
	</div>
	<div class="bg-black h-144"></div>
</Layout>
